               <p>I <rs id="t17781209-5-viclabel36" type="occupation">keep the <placeName id="t17781209-5-crimeloc37">Goat and Star in Pall-Mall</placeName>
                     <interp inst="t17781209-5-crimeloc37" type="placeName" value="Goat and Star in Pall-Mall"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17781209-5-crimeloc37" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                     <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t17781209-5-off34 t17781209-5-crimeloc37"></join>
                  </rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t17781209-5-victim81 t17781209-5-viclabel36"></join>. I saw the two prisoners coming along Pall-Mall; the woman, Stevens, took up a quart pot, and she sent the little girl, Allen, to take up another; I followed them a little way, and then I seized them both, and took two of my pots from them.</p>
               <p>(They were produced in court, and deposed to by the prosecutor.)</p>
               <p>How old is the child? - Nine years old. I have lost fourteen pounds worth of pots within three months.</p>
               <p>[The prisoners did not say any thing in their defence.]</p>
               <p>ALLEN <rs id="t17781209-5-verdict38" type="verdictDescription">
